{"tid":2155648,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"保護傘人潮不再 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-08-14T02:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T03:35:08.000Z","uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c00ce6e1372c429d135a8a54e3ecac953e1adf31","tid":2155648,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:29:04.000Z","msg":"保護傘人潮不再 - 馮睎乾<br />\n <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&d=Bi55TGPCxKeiDoZ%2FBZgBR4jkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=38298cfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200714%2FPDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4%2F&h=0de20b1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200714/PDQ3V7SA3ZA6NG75WDXQULDQK4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今天香港人支持蘋果的熱情，令世界動容，但我作為風景殺手，卻想在這時提一提台北的保護傘餐廳，藉以說明「熱情恆心，缺一不可」的簡單道理。記得保護傘在四月開張，新聞所見大排長龍，座無虛席，光顧者多數是熱情洋溢的香港人。但三個多月後又如何？<br />\n<br />\n似乎沒什麼人留意，保護傘的Facebook專頁已人間蒸發（大概跟「國安法」有關吧）。專頁消失不重要，反正like數也不能當飯吃，最重要還是餐廳生意。據一位幫襯過的台北朋友說，餐廳生意不太理想，波動頗大，現時顧客也以台灣人居多。香港人的三分鐘熱度，可見一斑。<br />\n<br />\n當然，恆心是雙方面的，不能只要求顧客。保護傘是餐廳，若食物吸引不到客人（不管是否港人），就必須找出問題所在，不斷力求改進，這樣才是成功之道。同理，蘋果日報也必須持續做得更好，才能真正留住讀者&mdash;&mdash;順帶溫馨提示一下，自從幾星期前蘋果更新系統，屢有年長讀者問我「名采版專欄去了哪裏」、「為什麼你每天文章的網址都停留在7月14日」等等，這些IT問題至今仍未修正。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大把黃絲冇訂蘋果日報<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12f022d49db171c35c167a439b0f75bbb15c21e","tid":2155648,"uid":83609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:32:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span class=\"red\">據一位幫襯過的台北朋友說，餐廳生意不太理想，波動頗大，現時顧客也以台灣人居多。香港人的三分鐘熱度，可見一斑。</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n疫情下點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64e05a5e007c4db5a4818ddf9d4fac95c444895","tid":2155648,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:32:52.000Z","msg":"台北保護傘去後感<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2023724\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2023724</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保護傘問題 &rarr; 貴、衛生麻麻、冇服務、食物冇水準、附近競爭大"},{"pid":"52b3a908911285855e02c3530d59056e08614c93","tid":2155648,"uid":77137,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T02:37:05.000Z","msg":"台灣餐廳問點解咁少香港人<br />\n我係咪要問返點解香港M記冇美國人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97813e30e6b750598afe21c8751d11b52b28a193","tid":2155648,"uid":248863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:14:18.000Z","msg":"台灣而家係咪比我入境先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />三分鐘熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc9851684b7e3f72e645e08e835003bb6e9e1d9","tid":2155648,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T03:35:08.000Z","msg":"係咪屌在台港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}